{"tid":1610811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗戰十年，直至共產黨灰飛湮滅】","createTime":"2019-10-01T20:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T21:21:17.000Z","uid":266607,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"15988c6560c55f866ddd4459e5dbbaf9f7fbf3d4","tid":1610811,"uid":266607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:49:35.000Z","msg":"已經拉左2000人。<br />\n而我要提醒中共和黑警。香港單純15-29歲的青年人就有120萬人。三分之一係40萬人。百分之一係12,000人。我地至少仲有一萬個人可以俾你拉。<br />\n而且每一個30歲以上的真香港人都會用盡力量保護和協助我們。<br />\n我們十年之內都一定不會被消滅。我們來看這眼下的十年罷。<br />\n我們會讓國內所有受苦的人都一樣覺醒。<br />\n我們會讓所有人知道黨是黨國是國，是兩件風馬牛不相及的徹底不同的兩件事情。<br />\n然後要你共產黨和黑警。灰。飛。湮。滅。<br />\n2019,1001."},{"pid":"cbf0a10b7f4dd736601658fa8c2562f13014d264","tid":1610811,"uid":46309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:53:17.000Z","msg":"立此存證"},{"pid":"3721840ad33cb3a74e46666d8e2303edb7ea1049","tid":1610811,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:57:17.000Z","msg":"不受傷，不被捕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f5fcc6dc6b38fee2c0b9e45b8cdfc356bfaaf3","tid":1610811,"uid":33966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:00:13.000Z","msg":"來吧！這是最好的年代，也是最壞的年代！"},{"pid":"ba4a240f66fca73f841a9147c63c1a5d2a5bc53f","tid":1610811,"uid":304663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:04:34.000Z","msg":"real hongkonger !"},{"pid":"d94cfa3d1e2b90b16f337a0f981356257dbb0b5a","tid":1610811,"uid":155784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:05:50.000Z","msg":"同共產黨鬥長命<br />\n無一個暴政可以過到100年"},{"pid":"cf913256e55092ca2f288c81e2f4a55097130ebf","tid":1610811,"uid":9019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n堅持，堅強<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"